p: Analysis of variance (two-way ANOVA) followed by Tukey’s test or Bonferroni’s test and linear regression for IC 50 determination were conducted using the Software GraphPad Prism 6.0 (San Diego, CA, USA). Differences were considered significant when p < 0.05. Probit analysis was performed with 95% confidence interval for LC 50 and LC 90 determination using the software Statgraphics Centurion XV version 15.2.11 (Statpoint Technologies, The Plains, VA, USA).
